---
import { url, base } from '../utils/url';

const guides = [
  { label: '소음성 난청', href: url('/guides/hearing-loss') },
  { label: '근골격계 질환', href: url('/guides/musculoskeletal') },
  { label: '심뇌혈관 질환', href: url('/guides/cardiovascular') },
  { label: '폐질환', href: url('/guides/lung-disease') },
  { label: '직업성 암', href: url('/guides/occupational-cancer') },
  { label: '유족보상', href: url('/guides/survivors-compensation') },
  { label: '출퇴근 재해', href: url('/guides/commuting-accident') },
];
---

<footer class="bg-navy-900 text-gray-300">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-14">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <img src={`${base}/logo.svg`} alt="하온 로고" class="w-9 h-9" />
          <div class="leading-tight">
            <div class="font-bold text-white text-base">하온 노동법률사무소</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gold-400 tracking-wider">HAON LABOR LAW OFFICE</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400 mt-4">
          산재 전문 공인 노무사로서 여러분의 정당한 권리를 되찾아 드립니다. 무료 상담으로 시작하세요.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
          <a href="http://pf.kakao.com/_xhkxccn/chat" aria-label="카카오톡" class="w-9 h-9 bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-gray-900 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 3C6.477 3 2 6.477 2 10.857c0 2.757 1.65 5.187 4.148 6.697l-.853 3.186 3.668-2.426C9.589 18.43 10.78 18.6 12 18.6c5.523 0 10-3.478 10-7.743S17.523 3 12 3z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="tel:01023151579" aria-label="전화상담" class="w-9 h-9 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4 text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">사무소 안내</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm">
          <li><a href={url('/company-overview')} class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">대표 인사말</a></li>
          <li><a href={url('/specialty')} class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">전문 분야</a></li>
          <li><a href={url('/cases')} class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">성공사례</a></li>
          <li><a href={url('/location')} class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">오시는 길</a></li>
          <li><a href={url('/consulting')} class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">무료상담 신청</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Guides -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4 text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">산재 가이드</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm">
          {guides.map((g) => (
            <li>
              <a href={g.href} class="hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">{g.label}</a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4 text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">연락처</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-400">부산 북구 백암대로 1167-1, 2층</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
            </svg>
            <a href="tel:01023151579" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">010-2315-1579</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 17h2a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h6a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2zm8-12V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4h10z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-400">팩스 051-719-9608</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-400">jswcpla@gmail.com</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-400">평일 09:00–18:00<br />토 09:00–13:00 (일·공휴일 휴무)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom bar -->
  <div class="border-t border-white/10 py-5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-xs text-gray-500">
      <p>&copy; 2024 하온 노동법률사무소. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">개인정보처리방침</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">이용약관</a>
        <span>공인노무사 등록번호: 제2024-가나-12345호</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
